steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"3jtcg","text":"Use one, almost confluent, 6-well plate of hPSCs to prepare cell pellet","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"fmn9o","text":"Add 1 ml of 1 mg/ml collagenase solution into each well to separate hPSC colonies from MEFs. {"blocks":[{"key":"2f484","text":"Add 2 ml Wash Medium to each well","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"fi4rr","text":"Pipette repeatedly with 5 ml pipette to lift colonies. Be careful not to carry over too many MEFs","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"de8lh","text":"Transfer all colonies into a 15 ml tube","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"2squa","text":"Add 7 ml Wash Medium into the 15 ml tube. Pipette with 10 ml Stripette for 5 times to separate MEFs that are attached to hPSCs colonies","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3tlb6","text":"Place the 15 ml tubes on a tube rack and gravity settle colonies at   for  . {"blocks":[{"key":"c84r6","text":"Gravity settle at   for  .","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":18,"length":1},{"key":1,"offset":24,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"495lu","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"temperature","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"error_temperature":false,"guid":"5A8545800A4811EDA1C41129801017D4","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"temperature":"","unit":32}},"1":{"type":"duration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":300,"guid":"5CEA10800A4811EDA1C41129801017D4","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"start":null}}}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"da7b7","text":"Aspirate supernatant and re-suspend colonies in 10 ml Wash Medium","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"da4rm","text":"Place a 40 µm cell strainer onto a 50 ml tube","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"em8ku","text":"Strain the colony suspension from step 11. Keep the strainer since colonies are trapped on it. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"33jqs","text":"Wash the strainer with 10 ml Wash Medium (x2)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"9b88e","text":"Revert the strainer and place it in a 6-well plate, bottom-up","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"f9nrm","text":"Apply 5 ml Wash Medium to the bottom of the strainer, twice. This will separate colonies from the strainer and wash them into the 6-well plate. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"1i98l","text":"Collect colonies from the 6-well plate to a new 15 ml tube","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4ql8q","text":"Re-suspend colonies in the remaining medium, then transfer them to a 1.8 ml Eppendorf tube","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"5vhji","text":"Centrifuge the 1.8 ml tube at  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":30,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"bmrp9","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"centrifuge","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"centrifuge":"300","duration":300,"error_centrifuge":false,"error_temperature":false,"guid":"3695C9F00A4911EDA1C41129801017D4","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"scientificNotation":{"centrifuge":false,"temperature":false},"start":null,"temperature":"","temperatureUnit":10,"unit":34}}}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"efm8o","text":"Remove the supernatant and cap the tube","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7op4h","text":"Snap freeze the 1.8 ml tube by placing it in liquid nitrogen for more than 5 min. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
